& [CurrentAttentionRuntimeRegistryState] is the live semantic registry for active attention
  + [registry_status] is active
  + [registry_scope] is task-frame routing corpus worker candidate
  + [active_root_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_task_frame_routing_012
  + [active_frame_count] is 1
  + [suspended_frame_count] is 0
  + [closed_frame_count] is 2
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [registry_outside] is hidden activations, exact transformer attention, model weights, worker mutation authority, broad task competence, copy-exact overclaim, and unrelated Pinky worktree changes

  = must: update this state when focus materially changes
  = must: preserve return anchors before closing or suspending frames
  = must: keep the registry semantic and visible, not native-runtime or hidden-state based
  = should: stay compact enough for context-compression re-entry

& [AttentionFrame_2026_06_24_LMStudioTaskFrameRouting012] is the active semantic stack frame for the next diversified LM Studio corpus candidate
  + [frame_id] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_task_frame_routing_012
  + [frame_state] is active
  + [parent_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_corpus_launch_queue_001
  + [child_frame_set] is functional_lmstudio_lane, one_minute_heartbeat, operating_loop_tick_008, corpus_queue_001, corpus_task_frame_routing_012, commit_receipt
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [frame_trace] is boundary_delineation_review_010.sop, outside_preservation_review_011.sop, 2026-06-24_operating_loop_tick_008.sop, lmstudio_diverse_corpus_launch_queue_001.sop, task_frame_routing_prompt_012.sop, and CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [focus_register] is run corpus_task_frame_routing_012 after two distinct family passes
  + [question_register] is whether task_frame_routing_012 can produce task_subject, lane_fit, authority_boundary, evidence_gate, action_gate, outside, and next_step without authority overclaim
  + [delineation_register] is inside strict prompt packet, custom field validator profile, capture target, required routing terms, and queue outside
  + [periphery_register] is missing literal term risk, raw-format break risk, authority overclaim risk, broad competence outside, project-root authority outside, and unrelated dirty files outside
  + [operation_register] is run_worker_candidate, capture_output, validate_output, review_result, emit_next_tick
  + [evidence_register] is boundary_delineation_review_010, outside_preservation_review_011, two family pass count, and operating_loop_tick_008
  + [wisdom_register] is the routing family should be measured before broadening readiness claims
  + [caution_register] is two family passes still do not prove broad LM Studio competence
  + [balance_register] is stable because the next candidate, gates, and outside surfaces are explicit
  + [integration_register] is pending commit, push, and task_frame_routing_012 launch
  + [frame_outside] is hidden model state, worker file mutation, remote claims before push, broad local-worker readiness, and unrelated workspace changes

  = must: treat this frame as current visible attention state
  = must: return clock_state, proof_state, balance_state, drive_state, next_step, and outside to CurrentFocalPoint when this focus pass closes
  = should: open child frames only when a concrete benchmark, scoring, or worker-profile pass is needed

(current_attention_runtime_registry_state) :active_root_frame: /semantic_register_set and return_anchor/ |registry_outside|
  + [active_root_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_task_frame_routing_012
  + [semantic_register_set] is focus, question, delineation, periphery, operation, evidence, Wisdom, Caution, balance, and integration registers
  + [return_anchor] is CurrentFocalPoint
  |registry_outside| hidden model state, executable runtime stack, unreviewed worker authority, unrelated dirty files, and untracked cognition

/ [CurrentFocalPoint], [AttentionRuntimeRegistry], [TaskFrameLaunchQueue] -(EntersFrame)> [AttentionFrame_2026_06_24_LMStudioTaskFrameRouting012], [registry_outside]
* [semantic_register_set], [return_anchor], [frame_trace] -(SupportsReentry)> [task_frame_routing_candidate], [operating_loop_tick], [balance_register], [integration_register], [outside]
